{"tid":1655612,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再叫班保皇黨做建制派！！！","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T10:04:38.000Z","uid":33543,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5c768a657d49ad1922edbb54b3e0dcd537351972","tid":1655612,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"佢地從來都唔係叫做建制派一直以黎都係叫保皇(皇=政府)黨，親中派！！！<br />\n<br />\n一開始只有親共媒體同保皇黨叫民主派做反對派，而自稱自己做「建制」派，點解宜家個個都叫佢地做「建制」派！！！<br />\n<br />\n建制(Establishment)通常係指有權力係手嘅精英階層，而字面意思係指去建立制度。 <br />\n<br />\n所以一般廢老潛移默化就會覺得反對派(泛民主/民主派)係為反對而反對，而建制派(保皇/親中派)就係建立緊制度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以請大家正名返保皇黨親中派 唔好再跟佢地叫佢地自稱嘅所謂建制派</span></span>"},{"pid":"b9d31ba12beb2022133f30f6038048bcfcf0dde7","tid":1655612,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係呀,我知我地講近廢話,但前線的確需要支援</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n推 正名"},{"pid":"e5794aacd117d86adf742a363fbfee5b36c77d09","tid":1655612,"uid":70301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"其實我一直都唔明點解會用&ldquo;建制&rdquo;呢個咁正義嘅名詞去稱呼呢班仆街<br />\n<br />\n不嬲我都叫佢哋保皇黨/親共派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f6be3e4beaf30f89c0df50096877441fada5b5","tid":1655612,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"認同，而家連林鄭都直接講建制派建制派咁叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6804f0a87116e7b7ae471f218d4d830b48b2d7fa","tid":1655612,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"咪撚再叫班垃圾做建制！！！"},{"pid":"9b75d9d6801eda9b88c6b1790fd7388c51b3d291","tid":1655612,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:33:14.000Z","msg":"叫佢地 禍港派 / 親中派 / 親共派 仲好"},{"pid":"164aa479d7c1c0d8ed00cd22e6952caad4972d8c","tid":1655612,"uid":123933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:34:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">親中派<br />\nPRO-CHINA CAMP<br />\n<br />\n跟我講一次</span>"},{"pid":"84ad1736b75f7d710a6f912a91655b4b44b017bc","tid":1655612,"uid":326930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"[ 緊 急 ] 對 內 地 輸 出 文 宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656467</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"faaab572dfd21b82180b6a7f83d74e2b05dfe944","tid":1655612,"uid":210190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>奶共派</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9057fed1851199d8125e1c2640cb47bd324409","tid":1655612,"uid":120772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:03:30.000Z","msg":"奶共派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有佢地叫民主黨做反對派 掉轉咁佢地係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1601b2f407111625d43010c9dd31607792ee422e","tid":1655612,"uid":210190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d9057fed1851199d8125e1c2640cb47bd324409","tid":1655612,"uid":120772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime